# uritemplate

Generate and parse Uri templates based on RFC 6570. 

## Usage

as uri template creator:

(let [create (uri-creator "http://example.com/{role}/{nick}")]
  (create :nick "dfa" :role "user")) ; yields http://example.com/user/dfa 

as uri template parser:

(let [parse (uri-parser "http://example.com/{role}/{user}")]
  (parse "http://example.com/admin/dfa")) ; yields {:role "admin"
  :user "user" }

     	    
